      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without issue. While the exterior shows some minor surface scratches and typical stone chips from regular use, the interior is clean and well-preserved with no significant wear or tears. All major mechanical systems and interior electronics are in good working order, making this a dependable choice for a new owner.",
