      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, so it\u2019s in flawless condition without a single scratch or mark to be found. The interior is still crisp, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as cherished. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a look!",
