    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a seamless power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by precision-tuned individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers short, tactile throws, channeling power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential. Mechanically flawless, the chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
