    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, appearing exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear or creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. No accidents, no modifications, and a smoke-free/pet-free history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a specimen of unrivaled quality.",
